Zaida Navarrete Dudash

Zaida Navarrete Dudash

ZDudash@onesothebysrealty.com

(786)223-8365

Zaida has over 10 years of experience in the South Florida Real Estate Market and has been a Miami resident since the year 2000. She is part of the Eloy Carmenate Group, which is headed by one of the top one-percent producers in the nation, possesses a Business Administration degree and is fully bilingual in both Spanish and English.
Before working in Real Estate, Zaida’s professionalism and attention to detail landed her in the position of managing the Americas Region for the World Olympians Association. Traveling worldwide with this prestigious organization, she learned the art of catering the luxuries to the needs of her clients.
Zaida believes in having a close, personal relationship with her clients. “I spend the time to really get to know each one – their needs, the lifestyle they want to realize in a new home and their dreams; this way I can collaborate with them to find the perfect house or condo”. She takes special satisfaction in guiding her clients to be thorough in the real estate process and leaves no detail unattended. Whether you are buying or selling, from small beachside vacation condos to multimillion dollar homes.
Zaida’s integrity, warmth, sound knowledge, advice and diligence will turn you into a client for life!
